snippet: The FBI will help investigate the shooting of a Sikh man who said a gunman approached him as he worked on his car in his suburban Seattle driveway and told him "go back to your own country," authorities said Sunday....

headline.main: China Trims 2017 Growth Target, Warns Against Trade Controls
headline.print_headline: China Trims 2017 Growth Target, Warns Against Trade Controls

lead_paragraph: The FBI will help investigate the shooting of a Sikh man who said a gunman approached him as he worked on his car in his suburban Seattle driveway and told him "go back to your own country," authorities said Sunday.
